{"word":"G2444 - ἱνατί - hinatí - hin-at-ee' - Wherefore","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἱνατί</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hinatí</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hin-at-ee'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Wherefore</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Conjunction / இணைப்புச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"என்ன, ஏன் - இடைச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"for what purpose? wherefore? why? that (what?)"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2443 - ἵνα - hína - hin'-ah/2443\">G2443</a> and <a href=\"#/G5101 - τίς - tís - tis/5101\">G5101</a>; <i>for what</i> reason?, that is, <i>why?</i>: - wherefore, why.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}